{{!--
  Primitive-note callout. Renders only when content.primitiveNote is
  non-null (= the slug is one of the 12 core atoms per isCoreAtom).
  Companion to the service-layer suppression of addAnalysis +
  equivalenceTopology on atoms.

  Wording is locked at the service layer (single source of truth across
  all 12 atom pages). The doctrine framing lives in the glossary at
  #primitives-and-compounds.

  Constraints (preserved from the service-layer comment):
  - never implies "simple" or "easy"
  - never implies compounds are harder
  - never implies ADD valuation
  - never collapses movement semantics into scoring semantics
--}}
{{#if content.primitiveNote}}
<section class="content-section trick-primitive-note" aria-label="Core movement atom">
  <p class="trick-primitive-note-label">{{content.primitiveNote.label}}</p>
  <p class="trick-primitive-note-explainer">
    {{content.primitiveNote.explainer}}
    <a class="trick-primitive-note-link" href="/freestyle/glossary#primitives-and-compounds">What this means &rarr;</a>
  </p>
</section>
{{/if}}
